high_descs: Walk toward the counter, then turn left and walk over to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the metal fork off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the white table.
Put the metal fork in the wooden cup on the white table.
Pick up the wooden cup with the metal fork in it.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter with the coffee machine on it.
Put the wooden cup with the fork in it on the front left corner of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a wooden cup with a fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go across the kitchen to the counter, right of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the fork in front of the loaf of bread, on the counter.
Turn around and go to the end of the white table on your left.
Place the fork in the gold wine glass.
Pick up the gold wine glass with the fork inside it.
Go to the dishwasher just ahead, to your left.
Place the gold wine glass with the fork inside it, on the front, right corner of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass containing a fork on the dishwasher.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the fork on the counter.
Turn around and step forward and turn to the left to face the white table.
Place the fork in the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup with a fork in it.
Take a step to the right to face the table to the right of the white table.
Place the cup on the table to the right of the white table.
anns.task_desc: To put a fork in a cup and move it to the table to the right of the white table.
